ttp://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"tests\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"the company's VoloCity aircraft\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2055}, {\"ngram\": \"a medical rescue vehicle\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"once type certification\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year ADAC Luftrettung, one of Germany's largest air rescue organsations, agreed to customise two VoloCity aircraft for emergency medical missions, and add up to 150 more later, pending a successful test phase.\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2277, \"end\": 2281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ADAC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1635035301654917e-22, \"text\": \"ADAC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ADAC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ADAC\"}, {\"begin\": 2282, \"end\": 2293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_medical_services\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luftrettung\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_medical_services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_medical_services\"}, {\"begin\": 2302, \"end\": 2309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9999995740359734, \"rank\": 4.258534276212273e-07, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two VoloCity aircraft\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2386}, {\"ngram\": \"emergency medical missions\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"a successful test phase\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The VoloCity aircraft will be tested over a two-year period in the Idar-Oberstein and Dinkelsbuehl regions in western Germany.\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2601, \"end\": 2608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9999995740359734, \"rank\": 4.258534276212273e-07, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The VoloCity aircraft\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-year period\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"the Idar-Oberstein and Dinkelsbuehl regions\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will fly in Japan at the 2025 World Expo in Osaka,\\\" the company adds.\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2627, \"end\": 2632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Empire_of_Japan\", \"score\": 0.8425214587074302, \"rank\": 0.16454867883685234, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Empire_of_Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Empire_of_Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 2659, \"end\": 2664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osaka_Prefecture\", \"score\": 0.8030274824358116, \"rank\": 0.24527021648799563, \"text\": \"Osaka\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osaka_Prefecture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osaka_Prefecture\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2025 World Expo\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like the uncertainty it faced in Paris, it is unclear yet as to what kind of flights will be able to take place - be it exhibition flights, demonstrations, transport options or similar.\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2718, \"end\": 2723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.611246909731693e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the uncertainty\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2705}, {\"ngram\": \"what kind\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"flights\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2769}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"exhibition flights\", \"from\": 2805, \"to\": 2823}, {\"ngram\": \"demonstrations\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2839}, {\"ngram\": \"transport options\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As development continues, fundraising remains a top priority for Hoke and his team.\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2937, \"end\": 2941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoke_County,_North_Carolina\", \"score\": 0.978058559651503, \"rank\": 0.015444015444015344, \"text\": \"Hoke\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoke_County,_North_Carolina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoke_County,_North_Carolina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"development\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2886}, {\"ngram\": \"a top priority\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2932}, {\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like others in the eVTOL space, Volocopter is burning cash as it races to certification.\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 3044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2988, \"end\": 2998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volocopter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Volocopter\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volocopter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volocopter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2967}, {\"ngram\": \"the eVTOL space\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2986}, {\"ngram\": \"cash\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3014}, {\"ngram\": \"certification\", \"from\": 3030, \"to\": 3043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In late April, the company was confronted with a potential crisis when an expected German state loan guarantee of up to \\u20ac100 million ($110 million) did not materialise, leaving it to scramble for alternative means of financing.\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3129, \"end\": 3135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.999996491205155, \"rank\": 3.287491983058634e-06, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"late April\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3059}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3072}, {\"ngram\": \"a potential crisis\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3111}, {\"ngram\": \"alternative means\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3259}, {\"ngram\": \"financing\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It had already raised already \\u20ac500 million in start-up support for the costly certification journey.\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"start-up support\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3336}, {\"ngram\": \"the costly certification journey\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time, Hoke told journalists that declaring insolvency was not off the table.\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3389, \"end\": 3393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoke_County,_North_Carolina\", \"score\": 0.978058559651503, \"rank\": 0.015444015444015344, \"text\": \"Hoke\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoke_County,_North_Carolina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoke_County,_North_Carolina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3387}, {\"ngram\": \"journalists\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3410}, {\"ngram\": \"insolvency\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3436}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Volocopte